  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - 9 \u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fight for your rights - All come together on 9th - Senior Advocates request",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "In order to win their rights, the senior lawyers have called upon everyone to join together in the struggle on the coming ninth day, using the rights granted to the public under the constitution.",
        "In Colombo today (6) afternoon, a special press conference was held, and the President's lawyers and senior lawyers jointly put forward this request.",
        "The press conference was organized by the lawyers under the theme 'July 9 - 9.00 am - Colombo'.",
        "During this, President's lawyers like Shri Nath Perera, Sarath Jayamanna, Upul Jayasuriya and senior lawyers like Upul Kumaraperuma, Nuvan Boppake and other lawyers made comments before the media.",
        "'They are united to protect their power. Now we must all unite. We must succeed in this struggle,' he said.",
        "'The Rajapaksa family knows very well that if they give up power in the current situation, they will be completely destroyed. So we will all unite and chase them away.",
        "\"The Rajapaksas will bring in higher laws that will last them for the next two days, even if they go from being taken to hospitals to dying.\" In such a situation we should all unite' he said.",
        "'The legitimacy of the present government is gone. So use your rights to protest against the violation of people's rights. We are with you'",
        "'We are at the end of this worst economic crisis. Here everything is determined by corruption and crime. They do everything to maintain their power. So we can defeat them by coming together,\" he said."
      ],
